{{vgname|毛线小精灵|en=Unravel}}是一款由[[Coldwood_Interactive|Coldwood Interactive]]开发，[[EA|EA]]发行的物理解谜[[平台游戏|平台游戏]]。游戏于2015年6月15日在[[E3_2015|E3 2015]]大会上公布，2016年2月9日发行。本作的主角是由[[纱线|纱线]]制成的小型[[擬人論|拟人]]生物雅尼。续作《[[毛线小精灵2|毛线小精灵2]]》已于2018年6月发行。

== 游戏玩法 ==
游戏为围绕着主角雅尼展开，它是一个由红色纱线组成的苹果大小的拟人生物。由于雅尼身材矮小，所以它探索的周围的世界中，日常的小东西看起来很大。通过使用组成其身体的纱线，雅尼可以创造桥梁、拉动东西、在物体上摆动。它的纱线是用于解决复杂难题的主要媒介<ref name=Conditt2015>{{cite web |last=Conditt |first=Jessica |date=2015-06-15 |url=http://www.engadget.com/2015/06/15/unravel-ps4-xbox-one-pc/ |title='Unravel' is the adorable new game from a small Swedish studio |publisher=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |accessdate=2015-06-15 |archive-date=2015-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150615210220/http://www.engadget.com/2015/06/15/unravel-ps4-xbox-one-pc/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Corriea2015>{{cite web |last=Corriea |first=Alexa Ray |date=2015-06-15 |url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/unravel-is-e3-2015-s-most-adorable-game/1100-6428137/ |title=Unravel Is E3 2015's Most Adorable Game |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |accessdate=2015-06-15 |archive-date=2015-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150618014537/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/unravel-is-e3-2015-s-most-adorable-game/1100-6428137/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。雅尼移动时，它会用打结的方式创造线条，玩家必须使用它解决难题，推动游戏发展。如果雅尼走的太远而没有收线，它会逐渐散开至基本框架。游戏中的红色纱线球可以重新填充框架<ref name=Campbell2015>{{cite web |last=Campbell |first=Colin |date=2015-06-15 |url=http://www.polygon.com/2015/6/15/8766663/unravel-2d-stone-and-water-coldwood-ea |title=Unravel strings players along in a pretty 2D world of stone and water |publisher=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]] |accessdate=2015-06-15 |archive-date=2015-06-27 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20150627224730/http://www.polygon.com/2015/6/15/8766663/unravel-2d-stone-and-water-coldwood-ea |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 故事 ==
游戏开头，有一位老太太看着窗外，之后她调整了一名婴儿的照片，并拿起盛有毛线球的篮子上楼。在上楼时，篮子中的一个毛线球滚下来。游戏主角——由红色纱线形成的拟人生物雅尼（Yarny）——走进了屏幕中，并好奇地观察着周围的环境<ref name="Karmali2015">{{cite web|last = Karmali|first = Luke|date = 2015-06-17|url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/06/17/e3-2015-unravel-and-yarny-have-stolen-my-heart|title = E3 2015: Unravel and Yarny Have Stolen My Heart|publisher = [[IGN|IGN]]|accessdate = 2015-06-17|archive-date = 2017-08-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170825065216/http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/06/17/e3-2015-unravel-and-yarny-have-stolen-my-heart|dead-url = no}}</ref>。据萨林所述，构成雅尼的红色纱线代表着爱，这一角色会在旅行程中逐一揭开游戏中人们所爱的东西<ref name=Corriea2015/><ref>{{cite web |last=Matulef |first=Jeffrey |date=2015-06-15 |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-06-15-ea-reveals-adorable-new-ip-with-puzzle-platform-unravel |title=EA reveals adorable new IP with puzzle platform Unravel |publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |accessdate=2015-06-15 |archive-date=2018-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612223728/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-06-15-ea-reveals-adorable-new-ip-with-puzzle-platform-unravel |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 开发 ==
虽然开发商Coldwood以往作品的评价并不好，但《毛线小精灵》向EA的[[EA_DICE|DICE]]展现了足够的诚意以便安排其发行<ref name=Campbell2015/>。随后在EA的2015年E3发布会上，游戏开发者和创意总监马丁·萨林公布了《毛线小精灵》<ref name=Karmali2015/><ref name=Plante2015>{{cite web |last=Plante |first=Chris |date=2015-06-15 |url=http://www.theverge.com/2015/6/15/8785785/unraveled-ea-new-ip-yarny |title=Here's the first look at Unravel, EA's new puzzle-platformer about an anthropomorphic ball of yarn |publisher=[[The_Verge|The Verge]] |accessdate=2015-06-15 |archive-date=2015-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150616062600/http://www.theverge.com/2015/6/15/8785785/unraveled-ea-new-ip-yarny |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

游戏本身尤其是它的美学，在其公布后受到了欢迎<ref name=Plant2015>{{cite web |last=Plant |first=Mike |date=2015-06-19 |url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2015/06/19/e3_2015_press_event_conclusions/?page=2 |title=E3 2015 in a nutshell: Hurry up Hoth, and plenty to Unravel |publisher=[[The_Register|The Register]] |accessdate=2015-06-19 |archive-date=2015-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150621123140/http://www.theregister.co.uk/2015/06/19/e3_2015_press_event_conclusions/?page=2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[VG247|VG247]]认为《毛线小精灵》是“EA展示的最令人印象深刻的视觉游戏”<ref>{{cite web |last=Saed |first=Sherif |date=2015-06-18 |url=http://www.vg247.com/2015/06/18/indie-platformer-unravel-gameplay-e3-2015/ |title=Unravel’s gameplay looks just as incredible as its reveal trailer |publisher=[[VG247|VG247]] |accessdate=2015-06-18 |archive-date=2018-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180818054007/https://www.vg247.com/2015/06/18/indie-platformer-unravel-gameplay-e3-2015/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。最初的反响也引起了其与《[[地狱边境|地狱边境]]》和[[索尼|索尼]]的《[[小小大星球系列|小小大星球]]》系列的比较<ref name=Plante2015/><ref name=Plant2015/><ref>{{cite web |last=Figueira |first=Matthew |date=2015-06-15 |url=http://www.lazygamer.net/genre/adventure/check-out-unravel-a-new-ip-showcased-at-eas-e3-conference/ |title=Check out Unravel – a new IP showcased at EA’s E3 conference |publisher=Lazygamer |accessdate=2015-06-16 |archive-date=2016-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160518152239/http://www.lazygamer.net/genre/adventure/check-out-unravel-a-new-ip-showcased-at-eas-e3-conference/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。游戏使用索尼的{{Le|PhyreEngine|PhyreEngine}}引擎制作<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.gamestar.hu/e3/e3-2015-exkluziv-interju-az-unravel-kreativ-rendezojevel.html|title = E3 2015 - Exkluzív interjú az Unravel kreatív rendezőjével|publisher = [[GameStar|GameStar]]|date = 2015-06-20|accessdate = 2015-06-21|language = hu}}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，开发商表示已在[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]和[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]平台开发<ref name="Dyer2015" /><ref name="Conditt2015" />。2015年12月14日，EA宣布游戏将于2016年2月9日在全球发布<ref name="release date" /><ref>{{cite web |last=Livingston |first=Christopher |date=2015-06-15 |url=http://www.pcgamer.com/yarn-based-lifeform-solves-puzzles-using-his-own-string-in-unravel/ |title=Yarn-based lifeform solves puzzles using his own string in Unravel |publisher=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] |accessdate=2015-06-15 |archive-date=2018-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180126235631/http://www.pcgamer.com/yarn-based-lifeform-solves-puzzles-using-his-own-string-in-unravel/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

游戏的背景和难题受到了[[瑞典|瑞典]][[于默奧|于默奥]]景观的启发。萨林在瑞典北部的一次家庭露营之旅中汲取灵感，用轮胎钢丝和纱线做了一个雅尼娃娃<ref>{{cite web |last=Mitre |first=Dan |date=2015-06-15 |url=http://blog.us.playstation.com/2015/06/15/introducing-unravel-coming-to-ps4/ |title=Introducing Unravel, Coming to PS4 |publisher=[[PlayStation_Blog|PlayStation Blog]] |accessdate=2015-06-15 |archive-date=2015-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150618052349/http://blog.us.playstation.com/2015/06/15/introducing-unravel-coming-to-ps4/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Moore |first=Bo |date=2015-06-15 |url=http://www.wired.com/2015/06/unravel-e3-2015/ |title=Bit of Yarn and Wire Inspire a Delightful Puzzle Game |publisher=[[Wired|Wired]] |accessdate=2015-06-15 |archive-date=2015-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617234917/http://www.wired.com/2015/06/unravel-e3-2015 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 

2016年1月21日，在申请遭到[[美国专利及商标局|美国专利局]]的拒绝后，EA放弃了“Unravel”的商标<ref>{{cite web |last=Chalk |first=Andy |date=2016-01-21 |url=http://www.pcgamer.com/ea-abandons-unravel-trademark-application-after-uspto-rejects-it/ |title=EA abandons Unravel trademark application after USPTO rejects it |publisher=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] |accessdate=2016-01-21 |archive-date=2016-01-23 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20160123140139/http://www.pcgamer.com/ea-abandons-unravel-trademark-application-after-uspto-rejects-it/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。尽管如此，EA确认游戏将保留“Unravel”的名称<ref>{{cite web |last=Makuch |first=Eddie |date=2016-01-21 |url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/eas-adorable-indie-game-unravel-isnt-changing-name/1100-6434033/ |title=EA's Adorable Indie Game Unravel Isn't Changing Names |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |accessdate=2016-01-21 |archive-date=2016-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160123223120/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/eas-adorable-indie-game-unravel-isnt-changing-name/1100-6434033/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

